ualberta.g12.adventurecreator.views

Interface OView<M>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OnlineStorySearchActivity, OnlineStoryViewActivity

    public interface OView<M>
    An interface that all OnlineViews implement in order to be properly updated when the online task has downloaded all of the story titles and authors to list.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void update(M model)
      Called when the task downloading all of the online story titles and authors has completed.
      Should be implemented in a matter that will load all of the stories onto the screen and be able to hanlde when the download fails.
